ied to other velocity jump Markov processes, including stochastic\nvoltage-gated ion channels and stochastic gene networks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Apr 2013 16:56:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-06-12"}
