\ndelayed with respect to the plateau of SFRD_TOT and a likely origin might be\nfound in the evolution of the bright ends of the FUV and FIR LFs; 4) using\nassumptions (namely exponential rise and linear rise with time) for the\nevolution of the star formation density from z = 3.6 to z_form = 10, we\nintegrate SFRD_TOT and find a good agreement with the published SMDs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Apr 2013 19:59:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 May 2013 10:33:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
