berg theory. Among\nother results, we present a complete combinatorial classification for point\nconfigurations of degree 1. Moreover, we show combinatorial restrictions for\nconfigurations of small degree in terms of the novel concepts of weak Cayley\nconfigurations and codegree decompositions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Apr 2013 14:35:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-04-29"}
